{"tid":2115563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"匯豐調整全線營業時間 周一至周五提早1小時關門","createTime":"2020-07-19T14:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T16:27:04.000Z","uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0c66054907a651e6746e7bbd2e2c2553b526778d","tid":2115563,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"匯豐調整全線營業時間 周一至周五提早1小時關門<br />\n文章日期：2020年7月19日 22:40<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200719/s00010/0b10cf5fc0fa9d51ac53bbf9222506c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200719%2Fs00010%2F0b10cf5fc0fa9d51ac53bbf9222506c0.jpg&h=c9724398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1<br />\n<br />\n滙豐銀行宣布，由明天（20日）起調整全線分行營業時間，星期一至星期五將提早一小時關門，營業時間將為上午9時至下午4時，星期六營業時間則維持上午9時至下午1時不變。滙豐旗下三部流動銀行亦會暫停服務，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n同時，滙豐兩家分別位於觀塘及上水的中小企中心，將由7月21日(星期二)起暫停服務，直至另行通知。該行早前亦已暫時關閉三家零售銀行分行及一家中小企中心。"},{"pid":"c273f1994519cce954963285fd76a1bb5ead4470","tid":2115563,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"[邊個諗出黎］法院登記處及一般聆訊聆只停兩日，星期三恢復正常<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2115519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2115519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"60deef39b3064c61974a39611127c68368ef717b","tid":2115563,"uid":45518,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:55:12.000Z","msg":"4點至5點呢段時間病毒傳染力特別強"},{"pid":"9df4b3bccf935549eedd6d0742b4870adc98d14d","tid":2115563,"uid":39878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:56:43.000Z","msg":"因為要俾員工6點前返到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57731f671b2b5665c09516f157db59d23cb629d","tid":2115563,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60deef39b3064c61974a39611127c68368ef717b","tid":2115563,"uid":45518,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:55:12.000Z","msg":"4點至5點呢段時間病毒傳染力特別強"},"citedBy":0,"r